Package: globalPM25
Title: Query Real-Time Local Air Pollute PM2.5 Level
Version: 0.1
Description: Query real-time local air pollute PM2.5 level near you, at any city around the world or within a user-defined geographical boundary. The real-time data soruce is coming from \url{http://www.aqicn.org}. To use the package, users first need to request a personal API token from \url{http://aqicn.org/data-platform/token/#/}. After setting the token, users can query PM2.5 level near your current location, at any city or a list of cities worldwide, within a city region or a geographical boundary. 
Depends: R (>= 3.3.2)
Imports: jsonlite, tibble, dplyr, utils, ggplot2, stats, graphics, ggmap
Suggests: testthat,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    maps,
